# File Protocol (cross-repo contract)

## Output directory

```
~/.roduq/output/<client-id>/        # client-id = kebab-case slug
├── .complete                       # written LAST — signals CLI ready
├── meta.json                       # generation metadata
├── design-system.md                # human-readable summary
├── tokens.json                     # JSON Schema v1 validated
├── sections.json                   # JSON Schema v1 validated
├── content.json                    # JSON Schema v1 validated
├── preview.html                    # static snapshot dla verification
└── assets/                         # optional uploaded brand files
```

## Schema host

JSON Schemas hostowane w `schemas/` katalog (local) + production at `https://roduq.dev/schemas/v1/`.

Każdy output JSON file MUSI mieć `$schema` field wskazujący wersję:

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://roduq.dev/schemas/v1/tokens.schema.json",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  ...
}
```

## tokens.json (REQUIRED fields)

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://roduq.dev/schemas/v1/tokens.schema.json",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "generatedAt": "2026-05-26T19:45:00Z",
  "generatedBy": "roduq-design-generator-studio@1.0.0",
  "sourcePrompt": "<original user brief>",
  "selectedVariant": 2,
  "tokens": {
    "color": {
      "surface": { "default": "#FFFFFF", "raised": "#FAFAFA", "sunken": "#F5F5F5" },
      "ink": { "primary": "#0F0F0F", "secondary": "#525252" },
      "outline": { "subtle": "rgba(0,0,0,0.06)", "default": "rgba(0,0,0,0.12)" },
      "brand": { "primary": "#2563EB", "secondary": "#0EA5E9" }
    },
    "font": {
      "display": "Inter Tight, system-ui, sans-serif",
      "body": "Inter, system-ui, sans-serif",
      "mono": "JetBrains Mono, monospace"
