## sections.json (REQUIRED fields)

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://roduq.dev/schemas/v1/sections.schema.json",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "homepage": {
    "blocks": [
      {
        "blockType": "hero",
        "variant": "centered",
        "title": "...",
        "subtitle": "...",
        "ctaPrimary": { "label": "...", "href": "..." }
      }
    ]
  },
  "pages": {
    "/o-nas": { "blocks": [...] },
    "/cennik": { "blocks": [...] }
  }
}
```

**Block types MUST match** `apps/marketing-starter/src/blocks/types.ts` w roduq-web-starter (canonical source). NIE wymyślaj nowych blockType.

